body: Hi Xandrika, It is very similar to how you export it to EnergyPlus. I attached an example. [](http://api.ning.com:80/files/51GNwYDFQ0RFLldHG*4WOhLfG-03n469JWR0b51ACqX6Xsc9d1GQUiHnlgyyCoOvfu3JZ9ICK5mWgVQbuk4f1YAmJeq8ONyX/OpenStudio_Example.png) Be aware that OpenStudio libraries won't be loaded on some systems. We are working on this with OpenStudio team ([https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/issues/214](https://github.com/mostaphaRoudsari/Honeybee/issues/214)). I hope it works on your system with no issue. Mostapha
